                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030914-36-defend338 t18030914-36-punish218"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, <rs id="t18030914-36-punish219" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18030914-36-punish219" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18030914-36-punish219" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030914-36-defend338 t18030914-36-punish219"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
